OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome
OL,6,Fpersistent rain over North Highland
OL,7,Fthis evening turning showery from the
OL,8,Fsouth. A few clear intervals overnight
OL,9,Fbut still rather cloudy with a few
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FQuite cloudy but some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny intervals developing,
OL,14,Falong with a few showers which could
OL,15,Fturn heavy and thundery in the far
OL,16,Fnorth. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
